        <div class="question">


            <div class="welovestackoverflow" style="margin-top: 10px;">
                <div style="float: left;">
                        <p>
Stochastic processes (with either discrete or continuous time dependence) on a discrete (finite or countably infinite) state space in which the distribution of the next state depends only on the current state. For Markov processes on continuous state spaces please use (markov-process) instead.                         </p>
                                            <p style="margin-bottom: 0;">
                            <a title="tag wiki" href="/tags/markov-chains/info">learn more&hellip;</a>
